⍝ ZBus.Nats Key/Value Store test suite
⍝ Validates: bucket create, put, get, delete, watch
⍝ Requires nats-server -js running on localhost:4222

⎕IO ⎕ML←1
pass←1
tests←0 ⋄ passed←0

dll←'D:\devel\Z-Format\src\ZBus.Nats\bin\Release\net10.0\win-x64\publish\ZBus.Nats.dll'

⍝ ── Define ⎕NA bindings ──────────────────────────────────────────────

'zbus_init'         ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_init <0T1 >Z'
'zbus_wait'         ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_wait& <0T1 I4 >Z >Z >Z'
'zbus_close'        ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_close <0T1'
'zbus_describe'     ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_describe <0T1 >Z'
'nats_connect'      ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_connect <0T1 <0T1'
'nats_kv'           ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_kv <0T1 =Z'
'nats_kv_get'       ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_kv_get <0T1 <0T1 >Z'
'nats_kv_put'       ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_kv_put <0T1 <0T1 =Z'
'nats_kv_del'       ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_kv_del <0T1 <0T1'
'nats_kv_watch'     ⎕NA 'I4 ',dll,'|zbus_nats_kv_watch <0T1 <0T1'

⎕←'══════════════════════════════════════════'
⎕←' ZBus.Nats Key/Value Store Tests'
⎕←'══════════════════════════════════════════'
⎕←''

⍝ ── Setup ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

(rc rootName)←zbus_init 'KV' 0
rc←nats_connect 'KV' 'nats://localhost:4222'
(rc obj evt data)←zbus_wait 'KV' 5000 0 0 0
:If evt≢'Connected' ⋄ ⎕←'FATAL: not connected' ⋄ ⎕OFF 1 ⋄ :EndIf
⎕←'Connected to NATS'
⎕←''

⍝ ── Test 1: Create bucket ───────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←'Test 1: Create bucket'
(rc bucketName)←nats_kv 'KV' 'settings'
tests+←1
:If rc=0
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ bucket created: ',bucketName
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ bucket creation failed rc=',⍕rc
:EndIf

⍝ ── Test 2: Put values ──────────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←''
⎕←'Test 2: Put values'
(rc rev1)←nats_kv_put bucketName 'api.timeout' '30'
tests+←1
:If rc=0
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ put api.timeout rev=',⍕rev1
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ put failed rc=',⍕rc
:EndIf

(rc rev2)←nats_kv_put bucketName 'api.retries' '3'
tests+←1
:If rc=0
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ put api.retries rev=',⍕rev2
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ put failed rc=',⍕rc
:EndIf

⍝ ── Test 3: Get value ───────────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←''
⎕←'Test 3: Get value'
(rc result)←nats_kv_get bucketName 'api.timeout' 0
tests+←1
:If rc=0
    val←1⊃result
    rev←2⊃result
    ⎕←'  value bytes: ',⍕val
    ⎕←'  revision: ',⍕rev
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ got value with revision'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ get failed rc=',⍕rc
:EndIf

⍝ ── Test 4: Update and verify revision changes ──────────────────────

⎕←''
⎕←'Test 4: Update value'
(rc rev3)←nats_kv_put bucketName 'api.timeout' '60'
tests+←1
:If (rc=0)∧(rev3>rev1)
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ updated, new rev=',⍕rev3
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ update failed rc=',(⍕rc),' rev=',⍕rev3
:EndIf

⍝ ── Test 5: Delete key ──────────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←''
⎕←'Test 5: Delete key'
rc←nats_kv_del bucketName 'api.retries'
tests+←1
:If rc=0
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ deleted api.retries'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ delete failed rc=',⍕rc
:EndIf

⍝ Verify it's gone
(rc result)←nats_kv_get bucketName 'api.retries' 0
tests+←1
:If rc≠0
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ confirmed deleted (get returns rc=',⍕rc,')'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ key still exists after delete'
:EndIf

⍝ ── Test 6: Describe bucket ─────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←''
⎕←'Test 6: Describe bucket'
(rc info)←zbus_describe bucketName 0
tests+←1
:If (rc=0)∧((2⊃info)≡'KVBucket')
    passed+←1 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✓ type=KVBucket'
:Else
    pass←0 ⋄ ⎕←'  ✗ describe failed rc=',⍕rc
:EndIf

⍝ ── Cleanup ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

⎕←''
rc←zbus_close ⊂'KV'

⎕←'══════════════════════════════════════════'
⎕←' Results: ',(⍕passed),'/',(⍕tests),' passed'
:If pass
    ⎕←' ═══ ALL KV TESTS PASSED ═══'
:Else
    ⎕←' *** SOME TESTS FAILED ***'
:EndIf
⎕←'══════════════════════════════════════════'
